    {
      "chinese": "可是我剛剛勉強會寫！從此，我再也學不到法文了！只能到此為止了！我這時是多麽後悔！後悔過去浪費了光陰，後悔自己逃學去掏鳥窩，到薩爾河上去滑冰！我那幾本書，文法書和聖徒傳，剛才我還覺得背在書包裡那麽討厭，那麽沉甸甸的，現在就像老朋友一樣，叫我捨不得離開。對哈墨爾先生也是這樣。一想到他就要離開這兒，從此再也見不到他了，我就忘記了他以前給我的處罰，忘記了他如何用戒尺打我。",
      "ab": "amawna, malralradram ku driya temililr i! kuwaadru adri ku lra karuwa meladaladam dra Furence tilin lra! papalru kadrini lra. salaw ku salriesi kemianger. salriesi ku anger draku niranaranakan dra wari. adri ku muka i takesian aw muka ku kiyarubua dra ayam. muka ku kana inayan i Sa-re edaludalusa kana urelra! \r\n[===]\r\nidru ku tilitilin na, kinuretan temililr dra tilin, kaledri triniwatriwang tilin i, a garemay i, ilremes ku driya draku kinudrekudran kana rutu na miabak dra tilin tu aludrunan. garem lra i, kamawan lra dra alialian. adri ku maranger dra kiretinuwas kemadru ku ikiyaanger kan sinsi Hanmay. \r\n[===]\r\nmuka ku kemiangera dratu uwaburekan kadrini aw adri ta lra aasalr marepanau kantaw i, abalu ku lra a adrunu driya tu nilangtrian kanku.",
      "order": "2",
